Usage: report_double_clocking [-help] [-file <string>]
                              [-max_delta_delay <float>] [-nworst <integer>]
                              [-reverse_slope_limit <float>]
                              [-reverse_voltage_change_threshold <float>]
                              [-view <string>]

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-file <string>               # output file (string, optional)
-max_delta_delay <float>     # incr delay threshold (float, optional)
-nworst <integer>            # number of entries (int, optional)
-reverse_slope_limit <float> # min reverse slope threshold (float, optional)
-reverse_voltage_change_threshold <float>
                             # min reverse swing threshold (float, optional)
-view <string>               # view name (string, optional)